alerts.description:
There is a risk of light snowfall (Level 1 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: < 2 cm; in windward areas: < 5 cm; amount already fallen: 2-10 cm

There is a risk of frost (Level 1 of 2).
Minimum temperature: ~ -3 °C

There is a risk of severe frost (Level 2 of 2).
Minimum temperature: > -12 °C; local minimum: in valleys and dips > -15 °C
There is a slight risk of icy surfaces (Level 1 of 4).

There is a risk of frost (Level 1 of 2).
Minimum temperature: > -4 °C; local minimum: as clear sky conditions continued > -8 °C
